    <section class="dark-grey-text">
        <h2 class="mb-4" style="font-weight: bold;">Scan QR Code Online - From Image & Webcam</h2>
        <p class="fs-5 mb-4">Our QR Code Scanner is designed to be super fast and reliable, making it easy to read "quick response codes."</p>
        <p class="fs-5 mb-4">You can upload a QR code image or scan it directly with your device's camera. Our tool will quickly show you the information hidden in the QR code within seconds. It uses advanced technology to decode QR codes accurately, without any mistakes.</p>
        <p class="fs-5 mb-4">No matter what the QR code contains—whether it's a text message, a link, product details, a location, or any other info—our tool can handle it. The size and length of the QR code don't matter either. We've optimized our tool to scan QR codes of any size effectively.</p>
        <p class="fs-5 mb-4">Everyone can use our tool, from regular users to professionals like developers and webmasters. It helps you not only read the code but also verify its content. And the best part? It's completely free!</p>

        <h2 class="mb-4" style="font-weight: bold;">How does the QR Code Scanner ensure user privacy and security?</h2>
        <p class="fs-5 mb-4">Our QR Code Scanner is built with user privacy and security as top priorities. Here’s how we ensure a safe experience:</p>
        <p class="fs-5 mb-4"><strong>No Data Retention:</strong> We do not store or retain any data from the QR codes you scan. The information is decoded and displayed in real-time without being saved on our servers.</p>
        <p class="fs-5 mb-4"><strong>Secure HTTPS Connection:</strong> The scanner operates over a secure HTTPS connection, protecting your data from interception and ensuring a safe browsing experience.</p>
        <p class="fs-5 mb-4"><strong>Permission-Based Camera Access:</strong> The scanner only accesses your device’s camera with your explicit permission. You can revoke this access at any time.</p>
        
